The paper is about automatically generating image captions, which is a task related to computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The proposed evaluation metric, SPICE, is based on semantic propositional content, which is a concept related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also evaluates different models and datasets, which is a task related to machine learning (cs.LG) and information retrieval (cs.IR).
